properties.headline: Dense Fog Advisory issued January 24 at 2:20PM CST until January 24 at 9:00PM CST by NWS Milwaukee/Sullivan WI
properties.description:
* WHAT...Dense fog will reduce visibility to less than one mile.

* WHERE...Portions of Lake Michigan.

* WHEN...Until 9 PM CST this evening.

* IMPACTS...Low visibility will make navigation difficult.
properties.instruction:
If you must navigate, proceed with caution. Use proper fog
signals. Make sure all running lights are on. Remember to use
your radar and compass.

NWSheadline: DENSE FOG ADVISORY REMAINS IN EFFECT UNTIL 9 PM CST THIS EVENING
